{"tid":2323994,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[走資教學] Dukascopy瑞士銀行 無限制離岸戶口","createTime":"2020-12-13T15:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:36:05.000Z","uid":87235,"like":12,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ae7ff481e510e7f818ccd975e877e277c2eca2","tid":2323994,"uid":87235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"近期港共政府開始政治清算，係咁凍結人戶口，許智峯同家人匯豐銀行戶口都被凍結，係呢個越趨共產既情況下，搞到個個都擔心本地銀行存放資金既安全性，所以想向大家推薦一間走資銀行選擇比大家！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-bank-vector-logo-e1598433704181-768x261.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-bank-vector-logo-e1598433704181-768x261.png&h=53de1ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDukascopy 是一間瑞士銀行，而 Dukascopy 銀行戶口是一個接受香港人申請的離岸戶口！它接受香港特區護照、手機號碼及住址申請，不需要 VPN，更只需用一部手機即可完成整個開戶申請。無任何開戶最低存款要求，大家可以開左了解下試用下先再決定資金放唔放入去都未遲！<br />\n<br />\n而且App界面算簡潔上手唔太難！申請 Dukascopy Bank 的戶口好處有：<br />\n香港人可申請｜不需使用 VPN，憑香港特區護照／BNO、香港電話及地址即可申請<br />\n申請門檻極低｜開戶不收費，不設存款下限，只需存入第一筆金額到戶就可激活賬戶<br />\n設有存款保障｜設高達 10 萬瑞士法郎的存款保障，即大約 85 萬港幣存款保障<br />\n可作離岸戶口｜總部設於瑞士日內瓦，可存放 23 種貨幣，如美金、歐元、英鎊等<br />\n可申請提款卡｜可選擇申請美金、歐元、英鎊或瑞士法郎的預付卡，方便提取資金或消費<br />\n提供線上客服｜設 24 小時的線上客戶服務，可利用手機 APP 或官網向職員查詢問題<br />\n<br />\n申請過程只花 15 分鐘，賬戶批核時間一般最短可一天內完成，最長亦只需 3 天。用以下邀請碼申請 <br />\n（已刪除）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>什麼是 Dukascopy?</strong></span><br />\nDukascopy 銀行 （杜高斯貝銀行）是成立於 2004 年的瑞士網上銀行，公司總部設於瑞士日內瓦，但在全球多個城市亦設有辦公室，如香港、東京、吉隆坡、里加、莫斯科等。<br />\n<br />\nDukascopy 既是銀行也是證券交易商，受瑞士金融市場監督管理局 FINMA 所監管，並為客戶提供網上和手機流動銀行服務，包括買賣外匯、股票、金屬、商品、指數、加密貨幣等金融服務。<br />\n<br />\nDukascopy 提供的存款賬戶設有 2 種，分別是 Multi-Currency Account 及 Private Service (Saving) Account。前者就是我們要申請的銀行賬戶，可存放達 23 種貨幣，沒有開戶收費，不設存款下限。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">資產保障</span></strong><br />\nDukascopy 的每位客戶都受到瑞士存款保險 esisuisse 達 10 萬瑞士法郎的存款保障，客戶不論是否在瑞士居住，都可享有相同的待遇及存款保障。<br />\n<br />\nDukascopy銀行網站：<a href=\"https://www.dukascopy.com/swiss/english/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukascopy.com%2Fswiss%2Fenglish%2Fhome%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=38ba0cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dukascopy.com/swiss/english/home/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">開戶教學</span></strong><br />\n在了解完 Dukascopy 離岸戶口的好處後，我們只要準備好手機及護照後，即可開始申請 Dukascopy 銀行賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">驗證電話號碼</span></strong><br />\n我們要先下載 Dukascopy Connect 911 手機 APP 以完成整個申請程序。打開 APP 後，輸入香港手機號碼及接收短訊，以完成驗證。然後就可以先填入推薦碼（已刪除）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-1-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-1-min.png&h=670b7a04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-2-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-2-min.png&h=1095a8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-3-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-3-min.png&h=8b30e49b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-4-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-4-min.png&h=ffa80d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（已刪除）<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-8-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-8-min.png&h=faa24095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">提交個人資料</span></strong><br />\n按下立即開戶後，即可依指示拍攝及提交個人護照（BNO 或香港特區護照），並逐步填入所有個人資料，即可完成提交 Dukascopy 的戶口申請。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-8-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-8-min.png&h=faa24095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-9-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-9-min.png&h=61070cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-10-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-10-min.png&h=5f22d968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-11-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-11-min.png&h=c4879507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-12-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-12-min.png&h=b31947f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-13-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-13-min.png&h=28bc0b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-14-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-14-min.png&h=5c24e217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">進行視像通話</span></strong><br />\n然後，我們需要再進行一個視像通話以核實身份。過程中，職員問了我 2 條問題：<br />\n你的姓名是？<br />\n你的出生日期是？<br />\n再用手機背面鏡頭展示你的護照就可以完成視像通訊，並可等待戶口完成審批。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-15-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-15-min.png&h=c781ae78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-16-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-16-min.png&h=b01f7c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-17-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-17-min.png&h=2bba30e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-18-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-18-min.png&h=592eaf96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-tutorial-19-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-tutorial-19-min.png&h=c28be3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">登入銀行戶口</span></strong><br />\n戶口申請成功批核後，我們會收到電郵通知，點擊電郵的指定連結以獲取登入戶口的臨時密碼，並到 Dukascopy Connect 911 手機 APP 的銀行戶口頁面登入賬戶，及隨即設定新密碼。完成後，便已成功開設了 Dukascopy 銀行戶口了！<br />\n如果有使用推薦碼（已刪除）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-login-tutorial-1-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-login-tutorial-1-min.png&h=dfcc3b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-login-tutorial-1a-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-login-tutorial-1a-min.png&h=822e52e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-login-tutorial-2-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-login-tutorial-2-min.png&h=a852e97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-login-tutorial-3-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-login-tutorial-3-min.png&h=33f7a510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-login-tutorial-4-min.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-login-tutorial-4-min.png&h=476f4c9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"952ce81c5290a935f97ab03deab210b54ea4da6d","tid":2323994,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a639096d44fcd0bca6810e4b2cbf4e2081d63938","tid":2323994,"uid":87235,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>匯款入 Dukascopy 戶口</strong></span><br />\n因為 Dukascopy 是一間位於瑞士的銀行，而我開的也是一個離岸的戶口，所以匯款的動作是必須要的！而且要激活 Dukascopy 戶口就必須先存入第一筆款項，金額不限。<br />\n<br />\n從香港匯款到外地，一般可以經傳統銀行進行電匯，但成本通常較高；也可以選擇經TransferWise 網上匯款平台，手續費及匯率較透明，匯款所需的手續費也較低。另外，更方便的方法是直接以信用卡付款，但會有約 3% 的手續費。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">以 TransferWise 匯款</span></strong><br />\n我們可以申請一個 TransferWise 戶口進行匯款，以減低匯款時所產生的手續費。TransferWise 是提供跨境匯款服務的網上平台，它為客戶匯款時會使用市場匯率，並無提高匯價，亦只會按照匯款金額收取指定百分比的手續費。所以使用 TransferWise 進行匯款的成本，一般會比銀行便宜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Dukas-Deposit-Money-min-426x450.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FDukas-Deposit-Money-min-426x450.png&h=6bf80d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n使用 TransferWise 匯款 HK$100，並轉為歐元存入 Dukascopy 歐元賬戶。<br />\n使用 TransferWise 進行小額的跨境匯款交易，匯款 HK$100 的歐元到 Dukascopy 歐元賬戶，TransferWise 的手續收費只需 HK$5.45，相比使用匯豐銀行網上理財進行匯款每次收費為 HK$50 便宜很多。<br />\n<br />\n另外，匯入歐元到 Dukascopy 亦沒有被中間行收取任何服務費，TransferWise 所顯示的 10.32 歐元能整筆完封不動地存入 Dukascopy 賬戶內。<br />\n<br />\nTransferWise網站：<a href=\"https://transferwise.com/zh-hk/send-money/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferwise.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fsend-money%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=0a1f9996\" target=\"_blank\">https://transferwise.com/zh-hk/send-money/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">總結</span></strong><br />\n瑞士 Dukascopy 的銀行戶口是一個接受香港人申請的離岸戶口，它接受香港特區護照申請，不需要 VPN，也不需要外國電話和地址。而且開戶不需收費，又不設存款下限，實在是為香港人走資提供了多一項選擇。<br />\n基於以上種種誘因，即使是戶口設有每季存款上限及預設較小的總存款額，但它仍是離岸戶口的很好選擇。<br />\n個人而言，Dukascopy 戶口會是我分散存放離岸資金的一個選擇，並且會優先選擇存放歐元或瑞士法郎！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">相關連結 :</span></strong><br />\nDukascopy銀行網站：<a href=\"https://www.dukascopy.com/swiss/english/home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dukascopy.com%2Fswiss%2Fenglish%2Fhome%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=38ba0cae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dukascopy.com/swiss/english/home/</a><br />\n<br />\nApp Store：<br />\nDukascopy Connect 911 App<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dukascopy-connect-911/id830583192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fdukascopy-connect-911%2Fid830583192&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=ccde0c2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dukascopy-connect-911/id830583192</a><br />\n<br />\nDukascopy App<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/dukascopy-swiss-mobile-bank/id1414311580 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fdukascopy-swiss-mobile-bank%2Fid1414311580%20&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=532ec4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/dukascopy-swiss-mobile-bank/id1414311580 </a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play :<br />\nDukascopy Connect 911<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.iswfx.connect&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dair.com.iswfx.connect%26hl%3Dzh_HK%26gl%3DUS&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=10c19806\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.iswfx.connect&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US</a><br />\n<br />\nDukascopy App<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dukascopy.swissbank&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dukascopy.swissbank%26hl%3Dzh_HK%26gl%3DUS&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=d41b0b45\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dukascopy.swissbank&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US</a><br />\n<br />\n教學流程轉貼至：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.flyasia.co/2020/09/03/dukascopy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2F2020%2F09%2F03%2Fdukascopy%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b0e123c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.flyasia.co/2020/09/03/dukascopy/</a>"},{"pid":"7cb280f1a79ebf9c745a2642c62dc99562891cbc","tid":2323994,"uid":206737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88eeafeb9620cc13307d93bc2802fff5131a9ac0","tid":2323994,"uid":40415,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>什麼是 Dukascopy?<br />\nDukascopy 銀行 （杜高斯貝銀行）是成立於 2004 年的瑞士網上銀行，公司總部設於瑞士日內瓦，但在全球多個城市亦設有辦公室，如<span class=\"orange\">香港</span>、東京、吉隆坡、里加、莫斯科等。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"2a651e1dfbe61be3f35ca4996cf63691dde638cd","tid":2323994,"uid":87235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">存款限額</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.flyasia.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/dukascopy-Limit-min-e1598510039308-413x450.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyasia.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2Fdukascopy-Limit-min-e1598510039308-413x450.png&h=0e4c75c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以登入 Dukascopy APP 後，按左上角功能表，選取 Limit 查閱戶口限額。<br />\n另外，存款時也需要留意我們所開設的 Multi-Currency Account 有 2 項限額：<br />\n<br />\n季度存款限額｜每 3 個月內可存入賬戶內的最高金額；<br />\n總存款限額｜在你的賬戶中的存款上限。<br />\n<br />\nMulti-Currency Account 一般都被預設為 US$5,000 季度存款限額 及 US$50,000  總存款限額。不過，你仍可以透過 Dukascopy Connect 911 手機 APP 或電郵向 Dukascopy 提出加大限額的請求。在提交了你每月收入證明的情況下，有機會將季度存款限額提高到你每月收入的 450％。或在提交相關證明，亦有機會可以將總存款限額提高到 US$100,000。"},{"pid":"e75e49fc682944de4a5bd68805688506940f7fe0","tid":2323994,"uid":225129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗幫f字頭嘅公司賣埋廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69511abd21e2ab53472059f4dd8be4fcb8182d2e","tid":2323994,"uid":276273,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"瑞士係可以比支那人員入境執法，<br />\n離岸戶口仲揾係瑞士?<br />\n你仲未清楚風險?"},{"pid":"9296805e7cdca81b50f068ff3f3249244bdefa0f","tid":2323994,"uid":40415,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6951